EscapeHatchIsHatchOpenTest
├── when epoch is not within ACTIVE_DURATION of hatch start
│   └── it should return (false, address(0))
└── when epoch is within ACTIVE_DURATION of hatch start
    ├── given no proposer designated
    │   └── it should return (false, address(0))
    └── given proposer is designated
        └── it should return (true, proposer)
